OL,3,CMan killed and two children injured in
OL,4,Ccrash
OL,6,FPolice have confirmed a man has died
OL,7,Fand two children remain in hospital
OL,8,Fafter a crash in Co Antrim on Tuesday.
OL,10,FHe was Connor McNeill, who was 41
OL,11,Fyears old and from the Glenarm area.
OL,13,FCouncillor Beth Adgar of the DUP
OL,14,Foffered her condolences to the family.
OL,15,FShe said the deceased was father to
OL,16,Fthe two young children involved.
OL,18,FThe single vehicle crash happened on
OL,19,Fthe Carnlough Road, Broughshane at
OL,20,Faround 3.30pm.
