OL,6,FPolice said Connor was driving a grey
OL,7,FNissan X-Trail when it crashed.
OL,9,F"Sadly, Connor was pronounced dead at
OL,10,Fthe scene and two young children,
OL,11,Fpassengers in the car, were taken to
OL,12,Fhospital following the collision where
OL,13,Fthey remain receiving treatment for
OL,14,Finjuries which are not believed to be
OL,15,Flife threatening.
OL,17,F"Carnlough Road was closed for a
OL,18,Fnumber of hours following the
OL,19,Fcollision and has now re-opened.
