OL,6,FDfI and PSNI meet to discuss potential
OL,7,Froad safety improvements on A5
OL,8,Ffollowing the tragic loss of Connor.
OL,10,FChief Superintendent Sam Donaldson,
OL,11,FOperational Support Department said:
OL,12,F"said that the number of lives lost on
OL,13,Four roads is unacceptable by any
OL,14,Fmeasure as I've already said 22 so far
OL,15,Fthis year and 71 last year. But they
OL,16,Fare not just a statistic. "
OL,18,FMinister John O'Dowd began by
OL,19,Fextending his condolences to the
OL,20,Ffamilies who have lost loved ones on
OL,21,Fthe roads.
